Volvo May Be Interested in Iveco Daily, Sole Says

-- B y   E l i s a   M a r t i n u z z i   a n d   S o n i a   S i r l e t t i
-- 
2011-06-03T10:19:51Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-03/volvo-may-be-interested-in-iveco-daily-sole-says-correct-.html
(Corrects to say  Volvo AB (VOLVB) ’s Renault unit.)  Volvo AB’s Stefano Chmielewski, head
of the Renault truck unit, said the company would be interested
in buying the Daily range of light trucks produced by Fiat
Industrial SpA’s Iveco division, if it were for sale, according
to an interview published by  Il Sole 24 Ore  today.  To contact the reporters on this story:
Elisa Martinuzzi in Milan at 
